WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 16]

02:50.150 --> 02:52.000
But I want something.

02:52.470 --> 02:53.400
What is it?

02:54.650 --> 02:55.960
The Weak Water Stone.

03:09.840 --> 03:10.840
No problem.

03:11.360 --> 03:13.220
I'll give it to you in three days.

03:18.700 --> 03:19.430
Master.

03:19.460 --> 03:21.520
Didn't I tell you to leave?

03:21.540 --> 03:23.079
There's a human girl

03:23.440 --> 03:25.640
who claims to be a friend of the Master of Bright Moon's.

03:26.320 --> 03:27.600
No one dares to stop her.

03:27.720 --> 03:28.840
Shall we let her in?

03:39.020 --> 03:40.110
No fight

03:40.190 --> 03:41.260
broke out?

03:50.720 --> 03:51.600
This must be Ms. Bai,

03:51.620 --> 03:53.900
the one carrying the Contemplation Stone.

03:54.140 --> 03:55.860
I finally see you in person.

04:02.230 --> 04:03.540
Who allowed you to come?

04:03.590 --> 04:05.500
I know why you're here.

04:05.550 --> 04:06.840
Let's go back and talk.

04:06.860 --> 04:07.700
Don't take unnecessary risks.

04:08.380 --> 04:10.100
Ms. Bai, you came at the right time.

04:10.430 --> 04:13.470
Master Fan just agreed to stay here for three days.

04:13.570 --> 04:14.520
Since you're here,

04:14.520 --> 04:15.900
why not stay for a few days too?

04:15.930 --> 04:16.930
Chang Wu,

04:16.950 --> 04:19.070
escort our two honored guests to rest.

04:19.399 --> 04:20.700
Treat them with care.

04:21.040 --> 04:21.720
Yes.

04:33.020 --> 04:34.940
This is getting interesting.

04:38.940 --> 04:39.860
Huo,

04:39.890 --> 04:42.040
my aunt was a bit harsh earlier,

04:42.060 --> 04:42.820
but it wasn't about you.

04:42.850 --> 04:43.600
It was because of me.

04:43.630 --> 04:45.360
So don't take it to heart.

04:45.380 --> 04:46.409
You'll know in time

04:46.440 --> 04:48.030
what kind of person she is.

04:48.500 --> 04:50.690
Why would I need to know what kind of person she is?

04:50.710 --> 04:52.760
The three main demon branches rarely interact.

04:52.790 --> 04:53.820
If she doesn't like me,

04:53.840 --> 04:55.010
it's alright.

04:55.540 --> 04:56.659
I'll just never see her again.

04:57.370 --> 04:58.250
But...

04:58.280 --> 04:59.720
We're going to be family after all.

04:59.740 --> 05:00.420
Besides,

05:00.450 --> 05:02.410
my aunt is like a mother to me.

05:02.470 --> 05:04.140
You'll see each other often.

05:04.160 --> 05:06.720
You can't just ignore each other forever.

05:07.410 --> 05:09.240
What nonsense are you talking about?

05:09.270 --> 05:09.950
Huo,

05:09.970 --> 05:11.380
you've come with me to the Fox Clan.

05:11.410 --> 05:13.400
Doesn't that mean you care about me?

05:14.650 --> 05:16.600
Mu Jiu, you've misunderstood.

05:17.200 --> 05:19.710
I'm here because I need to do something.

05:21.100 --> 05:22.220
You need to do something?

05:22.890 --> 05:24.620
Have you heard of the Weak Water Stone?

05:25.720 --> 05:27.840
Weak Water Stone?

05:28.180 --> 05:29.450
Forget it. Go back.

05:29.480 --> 05:30.560
I'll go find it myself.

05:31.420 --> 05:32.130
Huo.

05:34.110 --> 05:35.350
I really like you.

05:35.380 --> 05:36.530
You're all I think about.

05:36.550 --> 05:37.640
I'm serious about you.

05:37.670 --> 05:38.320
Mu Jiu,

05:38.350 --> 05:39.790
do you even know what it means to like someone?

05:39.810 --> 05:40.890
Of course I do.

05:41.180 --> 05:42.230
I don't just like you.

05:42.250 --> 05:43.450
I want to marry you.

05:43.480 --> 05:44.790
I want to spend the rest of my life with you.

05:44.810 --> 05:45.980
Marry me?

05:46.500 --> 05:47.850
Just because I saved you?

05:49.450 --> 05:50.960
That's gratitude,

05:51.050 --> 05:52.159
not love.

05:52.450 --> 05:53.720
It's because of that gratitude

05:53.750 --> 05:55.130
that you've developed

05:55.159 --> 05:56.600
some fleeting feelings.

05:57.530 --> 05:58.310
But over time,

05:58.310 --> 05:59.630
those feelings will fade away.

05:59.860 --> 06:00.920
When your heart changes,

06:00.920 --> 06:02.250
you'll fall for someone else.

06:02.280 --> 06:03.510
The vows you made

06:03.510 --> 06:04.630
will end up meaning nothing.

06:04.630 --> 06:05.390
I won't!

06:05.390 --> 06:06.130
You will.

06:06.150 --> 06:07.300
Everyone does.

06:08.520 --> 06:09.390
Mu Jiu,

06:09.820 --> 06:11.050
you're younger than me.

06:11.540 --> 06:13.940
There's so much in this world you don't understand yet.

06:14.960 --> 06:16.930
There are many beauties in the Fox Clan,

06:17.020 --> 06:18.630
and there are countless demons out there

06:18.630 --> 06:19.850
who are far stronger than me.

06:19.880 --> 06:21.350
You and I just happened to cross paths,

06:21.460 --> 06:23.090
spending only a few days together.

06:23.120 --> 06:25.010
You don't even know my past.

06:25.460 --> 06:26.870
So don't make jokes

06:27.400 --> 06:28.680
like this again.

06:30.940 --> 06:31.860
Huo.

06:36.610 --> 06:37.540
Who told you that?

06:37.570 --> 06:39.010
It doesn't matter.

06:39.030 --> 06:40.380
Why do you want the Weak Water Stone?

06:40.470 --> 06:41.470
You met Old Turtle, didn't you?

06:41.909 --> 06:43.270
What else did he tell you?

06:43.290 --> 06:44.370
Do we really need to

06:44.400 --> 06:46.490
argue over everything we say to each other?

06:46.730 --> 06:47.490
Fine.

06:47.890 --> 06:48.850
I won't argue with you.

06:49.680 --> 06:50.670
In three days,

06:50.730 --> 06:52.600
Chang Mei will give the Weak Water Stone to me.

06:52.940 --> 06:54.470
But in these three days, anything could happen.

06:54.920 --> 06:55.680
It's dangerous here.

06:55.700 --> 06:56.500
You should leave immediately.

06:57.659 --> 06:59.310
Why is it so hard for you

06:59.340 --> 07:00.220
to explain things clearly?

07:00.380 --> 07:01.900
All you need to do is trust me.

07:01.930 --> 07:03.290
I can trust you,

07:03.570 --> 07:05.530
but trust goes both ways.

07:05.640 --> 07:06.730
Fan Yue,

07:06.750 --> 07:07.900
after what happened in the Outlanders' City,

07:07.930 --> 07:09.930
I thought things were different between us.

07:09.950 --> 07:11.770
But why are you still like this?

07:12.250 --> 07:13.650
Haven't you always wanted to know

07:13.680 --> 07:15.410
why Mu is better than you?

07:15.430 --> 07:17.020
I can tell you now.

07:17.040 --> 07:18.390
He's better because he held nothing back

07:18.420 --> 07:19.630
and was open and honest with me.

07:19.650 --> 07:22.170
He's better because we didn't have to doubt each other.

07:22.200 --> 07:23.230
Do you understand?

07:30.850 --> 07:32.810
Ms. Bai has got settled in.

07:33.570 --> 07:34.360
Master.

07:34.720 --> 07:35.890
Do you think the Master of Bright Moon

07:35.909 --> 07:37.110
is angry?

07:37.930 --> 07:39.310
Can't you tell?

07:39.330 --> 07:40.920
He's as protective of that Ms. Bai

07:40.920 --> 07:42.680
as if she were his eyes.

07:42.820 --> 07:44.070
As long as

07:44.070 --> 07:45.600
we treat her well over these three days

07:45.620 --> 07:46.900
and take good care of her,

07:47.300 --> 07:48.740
Fan Yue won't make a fuss.

07:48.840 --> 07:50.700
I still think it's risky to keep them here for too long.

07:50.909 --> 07:51.710
Master,

07:52.220 --> 07:53.990
why don't we just let Tian Huo go

07:54.020 --> 07:55.760
so we can get them off our back?

07:56.080 --> 07:57.250
It's too late.

07:57.270 --> 07:59.530
Fan Yue came here for the Weak Water Stone.

07:59.560 --> 08:01.030
Even if we release Tian Huo, it won't change anything.

08:01.050 --> 08:02.220
The Weak Water Stone?

08:02.250 --> 08:03.810
But 800 years ago, it already…

08:05.150 --> 08:06.500
What's between you and me

08:06.530 --> 08:08.060
is not known by the Master of Bright Moon.

08:08.080 --> 08:09.670
Once Jiu's matter is done,

08:09.700 --> 08:11.310
we can just give him some random spiritual stone

08:11.330 --> 08:12.290
and send him away.

08:12.600 --> 08:13.480
Besides,

08:13.510 --> 08:15.130
now that Ms. Bai is here,

08:15.330 --> 08:17.010
even the almighty Master of Bright Moon

08:17.040 --> 08:18.480
has a weakness.

08:20.480 --> 08:21.580
Maybe

08:21.600 --> 08:23.340
this could be the turning point

08:23.540 --> 08:25.780
for the Emotion Tree.

08:26.160 --> 08:26.960
Master.

08:27.800 --> 08:29.000
Do you want to use the Master of Bright Moon

08:29.000 --> 08:30.000
as a sacrifice for the Emotion…

08:45.320 --> 08:46.600
Ms. Bai.

08:46.720 --> 08:47.970
Master said

08:47.990 --> 08:49.420
you're a friend of the Master of Bright Moon's

08:49.450 --> 08:50.900
and an honored guest of Jingyou Mountain.

08:51.120 --> 08:51.970
This is a small gift for you.

08:51.990 --> 08:52.830
Please accept it.

08:54.250 --> 08:55.320
This is...

08:55.350 --> 08:57.030
It's clothing from the Fox Clan.

08:57.050 --> 08:58.320
Since you've come all this way,

08:58.350 --> 08:58.990
we'd like you to experience

08:59.030 --> 09:01.090
the customs and culture of Jingyou Mountain.

09:01.110 --> 09:02.540
Let me help you put it on.

09:35.910 --> 09:37.030
Chang Mei

09:37.930 --> 09:39.530
is Wu?

09:43.910 --> 09:45.360
How much longer must we keep killing?

09:46.410 --> 09:47.200
What's wrong?

09:47.440 --> 09:49.560
Still not used to these blood-soaked days?

09:50.300 --> 09:52.280
From the way you strike now,

09:52.310 --> 09:54.150
it seems you've come a long way from the pain you felt

09:54.380 --> 09:55.710
when you killed your first Eternal.

09:56.270 --> 09:57.630
You've adapted faster than I expected,

09:57.650 --> 09:59.900
transitioning from an Eternal to a demon.

09:59.930 --> 10:02.640
I can no longer go back to the past.

10:03.150 --> 10:04.530
Now that I've become a demon,

10:05.180 --> 10:07.790
there's no need to cling to being innocent.

10:07.960 --> 10:09.960
Do you think Eternals are innocent?

10:10.320 --> 10:11.960
Innocence can be faked.

10:11.980 --> 10:13.080
Just like in Ning'an City,

10:13.080 --> 10:14.440
when your master and the others

10:14.460 --> 10:15.610
erased the memories of the humans

10:15.630 --> 10:16.910
to cover up the truth

10:17.140 --> 10:20.260
and went back to being noble, innocent Eternals.

10:20.290 --> 10:21.930
Don't bring up the past.

10:21.950 --> 10:23.230
Even if I've become a demon,

10:23.260 --> 10:25.100
I won't join you in slandering Lanling.

10:27.420 --> 10:29.300
So you still care for them.

10:46.960 --> 10:48.910
It's that evil insect again.

10:48.990 --> 10:50.630
What exactly are you trying to do

10:51.160 --> 10:52.770
by feeding that evil insect?

10:52.790 --> 10:54.740
Do you know what a puppet is?

10:55.420 --> 10:57.220
Once the evil insect is fully grown,

10:57.250 --> 10:59.560
no matter how powerful the opponent is,

10:59.580 --> 11:01.190
it can control their mind

11:01.220 --> 11:02.810
and turn them into a puppet.

11:03.150 --> 11:04.550
So,

11:04.580 --> 11:05.910
it's not fully grown yet?

11:06.190 --> 11:09.100
When did you start taking an interest in things like this?

11:09.130 --> 11:10.410
Could it be that

11:10.810 --> 11:12.700
this is why you joined

11:12.720 --> 11:13.950
Cold Spring Palace?

11:14.940 --> 11:16.180
Just asking.

11:16.660 --> 11:17.820
You don't need to answer.

11:20.690 --> 11:22.130
I can tell you.

11:26.330 --> 11:30.450
To refine the evil insect, it requires the lives of demons,

11:30.480 --> 11:31.840
Eternals, and humans,

11:31.860 --> 11:33.090
999 of each.

11:33.110 --> 11:35.200
We've almost killed enough demons and Eternals

11:35.230 --> 11:36.630
and just need to kill more humans.

11:36.800 --> 11:38.950
The more you kill,

11:38.970 --> 11:40.420
the greater the contribution you make,

11:40.450 --> 11:42.100
and the more satisfied Grand Master will be.

11:42.330 --> 11:44.090
Who knows?

11:44.110 --> 11:45.260
He might summon you soon.

11:54.390 --> 11:55.760
Feng Yu, Yan Huo,

11:55.780 --> 11:58.190
deliver Chong Zhao's message

11:58.220 --> 11:59.500
to all Eternal sects.

11:59.720 --> 12:00.800
Tell them to carefully monitor

12:00.830 --> 12:02.870
the whereabouts of their disciples.

12:03.690 --> 12:04.570
Yes.

12:04.600 --> 12:05.570
Be careful.

12:07.100 --> 12:08.060
Jing Lei,

12:08.310 --> 12:10.220
take the disciples of our sect

12:10.250 --> 12:13.220
and head to the human cities under Lanling's protection.

12:13.240 --> 12:15.230
Chong Zhao's message says

12:15.400 --> 12:18.780
Cold Spring Palace's evil insect is nearing completion.

12:19.100 --> 12:21.540
They'll surely target humans next.

12:21.970 --> 12:24.810
Lanling has been guarding this land for years.

12:24.840 --> 12:27.910
We can't let Zhen Yu do whatever he wants.

12:27.930 --> 12:29.140
Rest assured, Sect Leader.

12:29.160 --> 12:31.440
If that old dragon dares to come,

12:32.080 --> 12:33.520
I'll definitely kill him.

12:33.610 --> 12:35.760
You must be careful.

12:35.790 --> 12:37.100
Don't act recklessly.

12:37.120 --> 12:38.650
I'll keep that in mind

12:38.970 --> 12:40.390
and play it by ear.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.440
Good.

12:42.020 --> 12:43.090
Go.

12:50.020 --> 12:53.140
Senior, you're worried about Chong Zhao's safety, aren't you?

12:54.950 --> 12:58.290
His parents passed away when he was young.

12:58.670 --> 13:00.470
If it weren't for the dire circumstances,

13:00.490 --> 13:03.380
I would never have sent him to Cold Spring Palace.

13:03.700 --> 13:05.860
He's uncovered such a critical secret.

13:06.910 --> 13:09.990
It seems he's managed to gain Zhen Yu's trust.

13:10.410 --> 13:12.930
But Zhen Yu is a cunning and ruthless man.

13:12.960 --> 13:16.500
How much suffering must he have endured?

13:16.670 --> 13:18.110
Chong Zhao is clever

13:18.330 --> 13:20.430
and righteous.

13:20.470 --> 13:23.140
What you've done is for the sake of the world.

13:23.700 --> 13:25.550
When the time is right,

13:25.580 --> 13:27.030
we'll eliminate Cold Spring Palace once and for all.

13:27.960 --> 13:29.070
Chong Zhao

13:29.160 --> 13:30.220
will return.

13:31.010 --> 13:33.130
I hope so.

13:34.020 --> 13:36.470
Chang Mei agreed so easily?

13:36.960 --> 13:38.930
I also find it strange.

13:39.880 --> 13:42.490
No matter what, the Weak Water Stone is a treasure of the Fox Clan.

13:42.720 --> 13:44.760
Chang Mei shouldn't have given it up so easily.

13:45.230 --> 13:47.510
And earlier today, when I mentioned the Weak Water Stone,

13:47.860 --> 13:49.450
her expression was anything but natural.

13:50.040 --> 13:51.720
Ever since we entered the Fox Clan,

13:52.020 --> 13:54.110
everything has felt strange.

13:54.740 --> 13:57.220
It's no surprise that Chang Mei wants Mu Jiu to inherit

13:57.250 --> 13:58.340
her position,

13:58.360 --> 14:00.490
but why did she specifically set a three-day deadline?

14:00.780 --> 14:02.970
For this, she even used the Weak Water Stone as bait

14:02.990 --> 14:04.570
to keep us here for three days.

14:04.860 --> 14:06.500
I'm afraid that after these three days,

14:06.910 --> 14:08.370
something big will happen.

14:08.680 --> 14:09.930
I think so too.

14:10.850 --> 14:11.890
I'll go ask Mu Jiu again

14:11.920 --> 14:13.040
and see if I can find any clues.

14:13.060 --> 14:13.850
Wait.

14:15.700 --> 14:16.910
I'll speak

14:17.430 --> 14:18.340
with Mu Jiu myself.

14:19.760 --> 14:20.690
Master,

14:20.710 --> 14:22.630
are you worried I might agree to marry Mu Jiu

14:22.820 --> 14:24.060
because of the Weak Water Stone?

14:25.050 --> 14:26.600
I simply hope

14:26.620 --> 14:27.690
that no matter what happens,

14:27.720 --> 14:30.050
you won't make a decision that goes against your own will.

14:32.470 --> 14:33.260
Why are you smiling?

14:34.160 --> 14:35.470
Master, you've changed.

14:35.650 --> 14:37.050
The things you say now

14:37.070 --> 14:39.180
sound more and more like something Bai Shuo would say.

14:40.340 --> 14:43.300
You didn't tell her the truth about her condition

14:43.490 --> 14:45.820
because you didn't want to put her in a difficult position, did you?

14:46.190 --> 14:47.790
You're used to solving

14:47.820 --> 14:48.750
everything alone

14:48.770 --> 14:50.170
and protecting others,

14:50.630 --> 14:53.270
but you forget that Bai Shuo isn't fragile.

14:53.920 --> 14:56.170
She's far stronger than we think.

14:56.740 --> 14:57.530
I know.

14:59.240 --> 15:01.530
She's no weaker than anyone else.

15:01.820 --> 15:03.970
So her path shouldn't end here.

15:04.970 --> 15:06.490
But aren't you afraid that hiding the truth

15:06.650 --> 15:08.360
from her will hurt her feelings?

15:08.410 --> 15:10.010
Heartbreak is far more damaging

15:10.040 --> 15:11.090
than physical pain.

15:11.510 --> 15:12.790
As to when I'll tell her,

15:13.460 --> 15:14.580
I have my own considerations.

15:22.210 --> 15:24.530
You came to the Fox Clan without permission.

15:24.700 --> 15:25.860
Don't act on your own like this again.

15:26.860 --> 15:27.710
Yes.

15:27.910 --> 15:29.140
I'll follow your orders.

15:29.330 --> 15:30.450
It's not just my orders.

15:31.470 --> 15:32.920
Your safety is important too.

15:35.310 --> 15:36.610
By the way, Master,

15:36.640 --> 15:37.700
where is Cang Shan?

15:37.780 --> 15:39.180
During the day, he and I entered the Fox Clan

15:39.210 --> 15:40.090
and split up.

15:41.360 --> 15:42.530
Judging by the time,

15:42.800 --> 15:44.300
he should be back soon.

15:46.380 --> 15:47.860
How strange.

15:47.890 --> 15:49.160
I've searched all day

15:49.290 --> 15:51.510
and checked every secret spot Master mentioned,

15:51.760 --> 15:54.020
but I still couldn't sense the Weak Water Stone's aura.

15:57.820 --> 15:58.650
Forget it.

15:58.700 --> 16:00.280
I'll head back to meet Master

16:00.610 --> 16:02.160
and let the smart ones figure it out.

16:32.430 --> 16:33.420
This is…

16:33.650 --> 16:35.100
the Weak Water Stone?

16:44.070 --> 16:45.430
Chang Mei is Wu,

16:45.700 --> 16:46.770
Ling Long's younger sister?

16:46.800 --> 16:48.330
The earrings she wore—

16:48.350 --> 16:49.660
I'd recognize them anywhere.

16:50.360 --> 16:51.460
That's strange.

16:51.520 --> 16:53.480
Ling Long only had one younger sister, Chang Mei,

16:53.510 --> 16:55.060
but Mu Jiu calls her Auntie.

16:55.320 --> 16:56.720
So who are Mu Jiu's parents?

16:57.610 --> 16:59.640
Back in Rong Xian's illusion,

16:59.660 --> 17:02.870
you were Chang Mei's guard, Qi,

17:02.900 --> 17:05.829
and Bei Chen played another guard, Ba.

17:06.640 --> 17:07.710
Speaking of which,

17:08.069 --> 17:10.030
why are those two nowhere to be seen now?

17:10.319 --> 17:11.160
Forget it.

17:11.319 --> 17:13.710
For now, Chang Mei's matter isn't related to the Weak Water Stone.

17:13.730 --> 17:14.589
No need to worry about it.

17:15.190 --> 17:15.950
Bai Shuo.

17:18.349 --> 17:19.790
There's something I need to tell you.

17:25.750 --> 17:27.510
The reason I'm looking for the Weak Water Stone

17:28.190 --> 17:29.050
is because…

17:31.170 --> 17:32.200
What's wrong?

17:33.240 --> 17:34.050
Bai Shuo.

17:50.090 --> 17:50.790
Bai Shuo.

17:50.820 --> 17:52.260
What did you see?

17:53.730 --> 17:54.800
Fan Yue.

17:55.190 --> 17:56.000
Don't go.

17:57.980 --> 17:58.770
Bai Shuo.

18:11.220 --> 18:12.020
Grand Master.

18:12.720 --> 18:13.890
The last time we met

18:13.910 --> 18:15.630
was in Ning'an City.

18:16.270 --> 18:17.650
But at that time,

18:17.900 --> 18:19.710
you greeted me

18:19.740 --> 18:21.430
with your sword drawn.

18:23.520 --> 18:25.040
Things have changed.

18:25.360 --> 18:26.680
Greetings, Master.

18:29.810 --> 18:30.570
Rise.

18:32.150 --> 18:33.470
The head disciple of Lanling

18:33.490 --> 18:35.940
knows when to bend and when to stand tall.

18:36.200 --> 18:37.060
Very good.

18:37.120 --> 18:38.250
I like it.

18:38.270 --> 18:39.510
But I wonder

18:39.540 --> 18:42.610
how much loyalty

18:42.640 --> 18:44.310
lies beneath this flexibility.

18:44.570 --> 18:46.070
You don't need to question

18:46.180 --> 18:47.420
my loyalty.

18:48.220 --> 18:49.260
You'll see it for yourself.

18:49.770 --> 18:50.440
Chong Zhao,

18:50.830 --> 18:51.680
mind your manners

18:51.680 --> 18:52.550
before Grand Master.

18:52.580 --> 18:53.380
It's fine.

18:54.050 --> 18:55.880
I only value competence.

18:56.090 --> 18:57.220
If he's useless,

18:57.360 --> 18:58.860
no amount of smooth talk can make a difference.

18:58.930 --> 18:59.740
Fu Ling.

19:00.810 --> 19:02.050
You turned

19:02.520 --> 19:04.830
Chong Zhao into a demon within a month.

19:04.860 --> 19:06.040
You've done

19:06.240 --> 19:07.160
a great job.

19:08.480 --> 19:11.520
I thought Lanling's head disciple would hold out longer.

19:14.980 --> 19:15.980
Turns out,

19:16.370 --> 19:18.180
he's just another spineless coward.

19:19.510 --> 19:20.220
Chen Ye.

19:20.740 --> 19:22.060
From now on,

19:22.750 --> 19:23.790
Chong Zhao

19:23.900 --> 19:25.930
is one of us.

19:26.050 --> 19:27.110
Be polite.

19:29.290 --> 19:30.710
So this is Chen Ye?

19:31.680 --> 19:33.220
I was rude just now.

19:33.260 --> 19:34.370
From now on,

19:34.440 --> 19:37.060
should I call you Divinity Chong Zhao

19:37.260 --> 19:38.770
or Demon Lord Chong Zhao?

19:38.920 --> 19:41.290
Since I've joined Cold Spring Palace,

19:41.940 --> 19:43.820
I am, naturally, Demon Lord Chong Zhao.

19:45.390 --> 19:46.630
Just get to the point.

19:46.650 --> 19:47.980
Don't be sarcastic.

19:49.690 --> 19:50.690
Grand Master.

19:50.710 --> 19:51.900
According to the spy,

19:51.930 --> 19:52.970
Fan Yue and Bai Shuo

19:53.000 --> 19:54.480
entered Jingyou Mountain a day ago,

19:54.960 --> 19:56.330
but there's been no word

19:56.420 --> 19:58.180
of any conflict with Chang Mei.

20:00.310 --> 20:02.380
If I'm not mistaken,

20:03.100 --> 20:04.030
Chong Zhao,

20:04.060 --> 20:06.180
you and Bai Shuo are old acquaintances, aren't you?

20:06.580 --> 20:09.650
If I were to send you to Jingyou Mountain,

20:09.870 --> 20:12.350
you'd have a better chance of bringing Bai Shuo back, right?

20:14.280 --> 20:16.150
Grand Master, your target isn't Fan Yue,

20:16.170 --> 20:17.180
but Bai Shuo?

20:18.400 --> 20:19.850
Fan Yue is protecting her

20:19.880 --> 20:21.760
only because of the Contemplation Stone.

20:22.690 --> 20:24.800
Once she's in my hands,

20:24.920 --> 20:26.730
he'll have no say.

20:27.610 --> 20:28.650
Chong Zhao,

20:28.680 --> 20:30.430
don't you want to

20:30.620 --> 20:32.340
prove your loyalty to me?

20:32.880 --> 20:34.770
I'll be watching.

20:38.430 --> 20:39.790
I won't fail you, Master.

20:49.410 --> 20:50.300
Her forehead mark has opened.

20:51.180 --> 20:52.310
She must have seen another vision

20:52.310 --> 20:53.590
from the Contemplation Stone.

20:55.870 --> 20:58.110
Could the new Contemplation appear in the Fox Clan?

21:00.330 --> 21:02.280
I must get the Weak Water Stone as soon as possible.

21:02.810 --> 21:04.030
Cang Shan hasn't returned all night.

21:04.030 --> 21:05.400
He must have encountered danger

21:05.400 --> 21:06.550
while searching for the Weak Water Stone.

21:06.810 --> 21:07.640
Tian Huo,

21:07.670 --> 21:08.970
I'll go ask Chang Mei.

21:09.000 --> 21:09.920
You watch over her here.

21:09.920 --> 21:10.590
Don't leave.

21:17.550 --> 21:18.550
Don't worry.

21:19.220 --> 21:20.890
I won't let anything happen to you.

21:24.960 --> 21:27.040
Master Fan, are you kidding?

21:27.430 --> 21:28.590
When Tian Huo went missing,

21:28.590 --> 21:29.590
you came to me for her.

21:29.590 --> 21:30.480
Now that Cang Shan is missing,

21:30.480 --> 21:31.640
you also came to me.

21:31.770 --> 21:34.530
Do you think Jingyou Mountain is the backyard of Bright Moon Palace?

21:34.560 --> 21:36.270
You're the one who's kidding.

21:36.360 --> 21:39.060
Cang Shan did go missing here in Jingyou Mountain.

21:39.210 --> 21:40.680
Since you don't know anything about it,

21:40.710 --> 21:43.080
I'll search for him myself.

21:43.380 --> 21:44.220
Fine.

21:45.140 --> 21:46.750
Master Fan, you're new to Jingyou Mountain

21:46.830 --> 21:48.670
and unfamiliar with many places here.

21:48.690 --> 21:50.410
I'll have someone help you search.

21:50.460 --> 21:51.260
Thank you.

21:51.880 --> 21:53.190
As for the Weak Water Stone,

21:53.410 --> 21:54.750
I have one question.

21:55.670 --> 21:57.410
Since you've agreed to give it to me,

21:57.720 --> 21:59.080
why wait another two days?

22:00.110 --> 22:01.630
It's only two more days.

22:01.650 --> 22:03.320
What's the harm in waiting?

22:04.100 --> 22:05.260
It's a treasure,

22:05.290 --> 22:07.090
so it naturally can't be taken out so easily.

22:07.280 --> 22:09.260
If you take the treasure away

22:09.350 --> 22:11.500
and Mu Jiu runs off with Tian Huo,

22:11.530 --> 22:13.030
how am I supposed to catch him?

22:14.040 --> 22:14.830
Mu Jiu has no desire

22:14.830 --> 22:16.830
to inherit the position of chief.

22:17.150 --> 22:18.310
Even if he becomes the chief,

22:18.310 --> 22:19.350
he'll still run away.

22:20.200 --> 22:21.640
I'm very curious.

22:21.850 --> 22:23.610
Why are you so sure

22:23.770 --> 22:25.070
that in just two days,

22:25.070 --> 22:27.160
you can completely change Mu Jiu's mind?

22:30.400 --> 22:31.160
Master,

22:31.190 --> 22:31.750
bad news.

22:31.770 --> 22:32.660
The Love...

22:36.960 --> 22:38.250
Since you're busy,

22:38.920 --> 22:40.610
I'll go look for Cang Shan

22:40.660 --> 22:41.750
and disturb you no further.

22:50.060 --> 22:50.860
Master.

22:51.780 --> 22:52.700
Today,

22:52.720 --> 22:54.150
I took the newborn foxes

22:54.180 --> 22:55.460
to receive the blessing of the Emotion Tree,

22:55.480 --> 22:56.800
but at the end of its strength,

22:56.830 --> 22:58.070
the Tree couldn't bloom at all.

22:58.330 --> 23:00.130
Some people have noticed something is wrong

23:00.160 --> 23:01.230
and are privately discussing it.

23:01.920 --> 23:03.410
Chang Sheng has gone to deal with it,

23:03.570 --> 23:04.680
but I'm afraid this matter

23:04.710 --> 23:05.750
can no longer stay hidden.

23:06.090 --> 23:07.250
I see.

23:07.570 --> 23:08.540
Also,

23:08.800 --> 23:11.120
Cang Shan, the one with Fan Yue, has gone missing.

23:11.140 --> 23:12.620
It's very likely the doing of the Emotion Tree.

23:12.970 --> 23:14.140
I'll go check it out myself.

23:14.400 --> 23:15.600
Keep an eye on Fan Yue.

23:15.850 --> 23:17.250
Don't let him suspect anything.

23:17.280 --> 23:18.080
Yes.

23:23.510 --> 23:24.670
Yesterday, I was wrong.

23:24.700 --> 23:26.130
I shouldn't have forced you to marry me.

23:26.190 --> 23:27.190
But I've thought carefully

23:27.220 --> 23:28.260
about everything you said.

23:28.530 --> 23:29.290
I like you,

23:29.330 --> 23:30.780
and it's definitely not just empty words.

23:31.190 --> 23:31.910
Yes.

23:31.930 --> 23:33.300
I'll say it like this to her later.

23:33.330 --> 23:34.370
What are you doing?

23:36.610 --> 23:38.070
I heard Ms. Bai is sick.

23:38.070 --> 23:38.830
I don't know her condition

23:38.830 --> 23:40.030
or what medicine humans take,

23:40.030 --> 23:41.550
so I brought everything I could find.

23:43.170 --> 23:44.040
Take a look.

23:45.680 --> 23:46.870
I'm leaving.

23:48.070 --> 23:48.860
Stop there.

23:52.290 --> 23:54.440
I heard from Master about the inheritance.

23:54.890 --> 23:56.540
You made a bet with your aunt

23:56.630 --> 23:58.910
about whether you could marry me within three days.

23:59.550 --> 24:00.510
To avoid being the chief,

24:00.510 --> 24:01.920
you're actually betting on me.

24:02.200 --> 24:03.090
Mu Jiu,

24:03.120 --> 24:04.250
you're so bold.

24:04.280 --> 24:05.280
No, no.

24:05.450 --> 24:06.570
Huo, let me explain.

24:06.710 --> 24:07.910
The inheritance has nothing to do with you.

24:07.930 --> 24:08.450
It's my aunt...

24:08.480 --> 24:10.090
Are you a child?

24:10.480 --> 24:12.480
Blaming everything on your aunt.

24:12.950 --> 24:15.240
Aren't you going to make me fall in love with you in three days?

24:15.660 --> 24:17.030
There are only two days left.

24:17.060 --> 24:17.860
Cat got your tongue?

24:20.640 --> 24:24.450
♫The person standing far away♫

24:22.990 --> 24:24.130
I know.

24:24.330 --> 24:25.800
Because of what happened with your parents,

24:25.050 --> 24:27.770
♫Don't be afraid♫

24:26.130 --> 24:27.970
you don't want to think about love and relationships.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.000
I also know

24:28.120 --> 24:32.350
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

24:29.400 --> 24:30.810
that no matter how strong someone is,

24:30.840 --> 24:32.560
there are times they feel lonely.

24:33.050 --> 24:39.690
♫Walk towards me♫

24:34.700 --> 24:36.780
I'm not that capable.

24:37.370 --> 24:38.450
I can't beat you in a fight.

24:38.480 --> 24:39.990
I'm not as good-looking as Fan Yue,

24:40.050 --> 24:40.940
and I often

24:41.360 --> 24:44.340
♫My heart feels so...♫

24:41.480 --> 24:43.210
say nonsense

24:43.240 --> 24:44.070
that annoys you.

24:44.400 --> 24:46.000
But the thought of being separated from you

24:44.770 --> 24:50.640
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

24:46.460 --> 24:47.200
hurts me.

24:47.200 --> 24:48.070
I don't want that!

24:48.920 --> 24:49.730
Huo,

24:50.610 --> 24:52.290
I really want to be with you.

24:52.320 --> 24:56.620
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

24:53.910 --> 24:55.190
I want to be with you forever!

24:58.990 --> 25:00.380
When we're both old

25:00.220 --> 25:03.620
♫You are my distant call♫

25:01.260 --> 25:02.530
and gray,

25:03.980 --> 25:08.640
♫You are my first and last♫

25:04.890 --> 25:05.890
if you turn around,

25:06.660 --> 25:08.150
you'll still see me here.

25:08.920 --> 25:11.180
Will you then believe

25:09.080 --> 25:15.110
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

25:12.100 --> 25:13.750
that my feelings for you are real?

25:15.430 --> 25:18.600
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

25:18.970 --> 25:23.170
♫Let's never let go♫

25:24.780 --> 25:25.820
Sorry.

25:25.940 --> 25:27.070
I've said too much again.

25:27.990 --> 25:28.910
I won't bother you anymore.

25:29.930 --> 25:30.740
I'll go now.

25:31.490 --> 25:32.320
Do you mean

25:33.960 --> 25:35.090
what you said?

25:38.850 --> 25:39.680
Of course!

25:40.090 --> 25:41.540
Then I'll help you this time.

25:41.810 --> 25:43.340
In two days, I'll marry you.

25:45.650 --> 25:46.720
A fake marriage.

25:47.400 --> 25:48.750
But after the wedding,

25:48.840 --> 25:50.160
you can leave the Fox Clan

25:50.560 --> 25:52.160
and live the free life you want.

25:52.460 --> 25:54.750
When you can truly take charge of your life,

25:55.050 --> 25:56.570
we'll talk about us again.

25:56.980 --> 25:58.120
Us?

25:59.880 --> 26:00.940
You mean,

26:01.130 --> 26:02.410
you're willing to give me a chance,

26:02.440 --> 26:03.240
right?

26:03.480 --> 26:04.560
Think whatever you want.

26:06.050 --> 26:07.360
Huo, rest assured.

26:07.570 --> 26:08.770
As long as I'm alive…

26:08.790 --> 26:10.180
No, even if I die,

26:10.210 --> 26:11.530
I'll always love you.

26:11.550 --> 26:13.160
You have my word!

27:05.920 --> 27:08.010
The sap of the Emotion Tree is getting

27:08.040 --> 27:09.230
more and more corrosive.

27:26.840 --> 27:27.670
Master Fan.

27:28.130 --> 27:29.610
That area up ahead is wild grasslands.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.450
The trail ends here.

27:37.050 --> 27:37.950
That…

27:37.980 --> 27:40.290
Maybe some young foxes came here messing around.

27:40.310 --> 27:41.570
Don't worry, Master Fan.

27:41.600 --> 27:42.810
There's nothing special about this place.

27:42.830 --> 27:45.290
Lord Cang Shan wouldn't have wandered here.

27:47.010 --> 27:48.080
Who's there?

27:55.940 --> 27:56.930
Cang Shan.

28:18.990 --> 28:19.770
Master.

28:19.810 --> 28:20.990
-Master.
-Be careful.

28:21.740 --> 28:22.770
No need to stand up.

28:25.180 --> 28:27.030
What exactly happened to you yesterday?

28:27.190 --> 28:29.040
Yesterday, I…

28:29.060 --> 28:30.650
I followed Master's order

28:30.670 --> 28:34.090
and searched all over for the possible hiding spot of the Weak Water Stone.

28:34.660 --> 28:36.800
But the Fox Clan's territory is massive,

28:37.060 --> 28:38.580
and I didn't notice anything unusual anywhere.

28:38.610 --> 28:40.530
I kept searching until night fell.

28:40.550 --> 28:42.100
I was planning to return to report to you,

28:42.130 --> 28:43.490
but at that moment,

28:43.820 --> 28:44.960
I actually found

28:44.960 --> 28:46.070
the Weak Water Stone.

28:47.320 --> 28:48.840
The Weak Water Stone?

28:49.580 --> 28:50.310
How did you know

28:50.310 --> 28:51.480
it was the Weak Water Stone?

28:52.700 --> 28:53.500
That's right.

28:54.550 --> 28:56.880
I don't even know what it looks like,

28:56.900 --> 28:58.620
so why did I feel like

28:58.650 --> 28:59.760
I had found it?

28:59.780 --> 29:01.640
Could it be an illusion

29:01.670 --> 29:02.720
caused by some curse?

29:02.740 --> 29:03.540
Maybe.

29:04.250 --> 29:05.150
Then what?

29:05.360 --> 29:06.490
How did you pass out?

29:07.320 --> 29:08.520
I can't remember.

29:10.630 --> 29:13.120
I only recall seeing a huge tree,

29:13.400 --> 29:14.160
and then...

29:14.180 --> 29:15.690
everything went black.

29:15.710 --> 29:17.310
After that, I remember nothing.

29:22.920 --> 29:24.500
According to the Fox Clan,

29:24.670 --> 29:26.850
you were injured by the corrosive plants in the forest.

29:27.040 --> 29:28.040
But Cang Shan is from the Stone Race.

29:28.070 --> 29:29.230
His body is very tough.

29:29.430 --> 29:31.660
Ordinary plants can't hurt him like this.

29:32.360 --> 29:33.940
Could it be Chang Mei?

29:34.060 --> 29:36.070
Why would Chang Mei harm Cang Shan?

29:36.200 --> 29:38.090
Even if she's unwilling to give us the Weak Water Stone,

29:38.570 --> 29:40.680
there's no need for her to deliberately hurt my man.

29:41.140 --> 29:42.350
Today, in the strange forest,

29:42.570 --> 29:44.060
I noticed something in Chang Wu's expression.

29:45.010 --> 29:46.290
It felt like

29:46.310 --> 29:48.230
someone deliberately moved Cang Shan there

29:48.250 --> 29:49.190
for me to find.

29:49.370 --> 29:50.730
If I'm not mistaken,

29:50.910 --> 29:52.520
the truth behind Cang Shan's injuries

29:52.830 --> 29:53.960
is the secret Chang Mei

29:53.990 --> 29:55.580
is trying to hide.

29:55.870 --> 29:57.210
It's that tree.

29:58.540 --> 29:59.500
Why are you here?

30:00.390 --> 30:01.200
How are you?

30:01.620 --> 30:02.520
I'm fine.

30:02.990 --> 30:03.940
Cang Shan is injured.

30:03.970 --> 30:04.970
Let me treat him first.

30:08.060 --> 30:08.700
Here.

30:15.260 --> 30:16.130
Let me do it.

30:19.500 --> 30:20.300
Here.

30:23.080 --> 30:25.420
Last night, I saw another vision from the Contemplation Stone.

30:25.550 --> 30:27.300
This time, it was in the Fox Clan.

30:27.490 --> 30:28.290
As expected.

30:29.300 --> 30:30.630
What did you see?

30:30.790 --> 30:32.510
A very, very large tree,

30:32.540 --> 30:33.760
right here in Jingyou Mountain,

30:34.100 --> 30:35.860
shrouded in eerie white mist.

30:35.890 --> 30:36.640
Yes, yes.

30:36.670 --> 30:38.680
The tree she's describing is the one I saw!

30:38.710 --> 30:39.470
That's not all.

30:39.490 --> 30:41.390
I also saw you walking toward that tree,

30:41.420 --> 30:43.000
and its trunk split open into a giant mouth

30:43.000 --> 30:44.370
and swallowed you whole.

30:44.740 --> 30:45.570
Fan Yue.

30:45.680 --> 30:47.680
Cang Shan must have gone missing there.

30:49.400 --> 30:51.250
With so many trees in Jingyou Mountain,

30:51.270 --> 30:52.340
how are we supposed to find it?

30:56.630 --> 30:57.510
Master Fan.

30:57.530 --> 30:58.940
That area up ahead is wild grasslands.

30:58.970 --> 31:00.240
The trail ends here.

31:03.130 --> 31:04.220
I might know the way.

31:10.050 --> 31:11.020
Cang Shan.

31:11.040 --> 31:12.950
Take Bai Shuo back to Ning'an City.

31:12.980 --> 31:14.500
Tian Huo and I will return after we're done here.

31:15.770 --> 31:16.590
I'm not leaving.

31:16.620 --> 31:18.270
The Contemplation Stone has shown me a vision.

31:18.290 --> 31:19.690
If I leave, how will you get the Contemplation?

31:19.720 --> 31:21.120
Then I won't!

31:24.720 --> 31:26.510
What are you talking about?

31:26.530 --> 31:27.440
Without the Contemplations,

31:27.470 --> 31:29.410
how will you break the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal?

31:29.630 --> 31:30.760
I'll figure out another way.

31:31.370 --> 31:32.280
Cang Shan!

31:32.640 --> 31:33.800
Take her away.

31:35.070 --> 31:36.460
-Ms. Bai.
-I saw it with my own eyes.

31:36.490 --> 31:38.340
You'll be in danger in Jingyou Mountain.

31:38.550 --> 31:40.310
And yet, at this critical moment, you want me to leave?

31:40.350 --> 31:41.830
What are you thinking?

31:44.590 --> 31:45.260
Master.

31:46.060 --> 31:51.020
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

31:46.270 --> 31:47.830
She's already asking about it.

31:47.860 --> 31:49.060
Just tell her.

31:53.850 --> 31:55.130
You're a human after all.

31:54.180 --> 32:00.040
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

31:56.140 --> 31:57.910
The more contemplation power the Stone absorbs,

31:58.170 --> 31:59.810
the more likely your body will fail.

32:00.020 --> 32:01.170
Last night, when the Stone was activated,

32:01.200 --> 32:02.000
you bled and fainted

32:02.020 --> 32:03.220
for the exact same reason.

32:02.500 --> 32:10.040
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

32:05.710 --> 32:06.830
I don't have the time to think about

32:06.860 --> 32:08.330
the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal!

32:08.760 --> 32:10.510
All I know is that if you keep absorbing Contemplations,

32:10.540 --> 32:12.560
you won't live long enough to break the Seal!

32:10.820 --> 32:15.840
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

32:18.790 --> 32:19.830
Bai Shuo.

32:21.340 --> 32:22.750
I don't want you to die,

32:23.290 --> 32:24.850
and I won't let you die.

32:28.700 --> 32:30.010
For my sake,

32:31.940 --> 32:32.950
leave this place.

32:35.310 --> 32:38.450
♫Across thousands of miles♫

32:43.260 --> 32:48.010
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

32:54.800 --> 32:55.560
Master.

32:55.860 --> 32:57.170
The Emotion Tree has run out of nutrients

32:57.200 --> 32:58.680
and even begun to harm people.

32:58.700 --> 33:00.240
Obviously, it has gained consciousness.

33:00.410 --> 33:01.750
How much longer are you going to

33:01.750 --> 33:02.880
delay solving this problem?

33:02.900 --> 33:04.100
What's the hurry?

33:04.390 --> 33:06.330
Even if you want to force me to die,

33:06.420 --> 33:08.630
at least give me time to arrange my affairs first.

33:08.660 --> 33:09.920
Please calm down, Master.

33:09.940 --> 33:11.660
Elder Chang Sheng didn't mean to offend you.

33:11.690 --> 33:12.340
He's just concerned…

33:12.360 --> 33:13.120
Shut up!

33:13.550 --> 33:14.910
If you hadn't helped her,

33:14.930 --> 33:17.100
the Emotion Tree wouldn't have ended up like this!

33:17.270 --> 33:19.600
800 years ago, the Weak Water Stone was lost,

33:19.630 --> 33:21.390
and the Emotion Tree lost its source of nourishment.

33:21.410 --> 33:23.380
No one in the clan knew about it.

33:23.410 --> 33:25.300
If I hadn't become an elder,

33:25.360 --> 33:26.890
I wouldn't have learned about it either.

33:27.270 --> 33:28.310
May I ask, Master,

33:28.340 --> 33:29.290
if you still remember

33:29.320 --> 33:31.250
the promise you made to me

33:31.270 --> 33:32.390
when I first learned the truth?

33:34.500 --> 33:36.070
I said,

33:36.340 --> 33:38.480
even without the Weak Water Stone,

33:38.600 --> 33:39.950
the Emotion Tree

33:40.030 --> 33:42.740
won't wither away under my reign.

34:05.580 --> 34:07.090
The Fox Clan is skilled with curses.

34:07.290 --> 34:08.120
If I were you,

34:08.139 --> 34:09.670
I wouldn't follow them so closely.

34:09.739 --> 34:10.850
Once discovered,

34:10.880 --> 34:12.250
you won't even have the chance to fight back

34:12.270 --> 34:13.670
before they knock you out with a curse.

34:19.570 --> 34:20.780
Why are you here?

34:21.260 --> 34:22.449
I was worried about you,

34:22.469 --> 34:23.630
so I begged Grand Master

34:23.659 --> 34:24.500
to let me come protect you.

34:24.520 --> 34:25.639
You mean monitor me.

34:25.949 --> 34:27.000
You were afraid I'd reveal

34:27.000 --> 34:28.719
Cold Spring Palace's secret plan,

34:28.909 --> 34:30.110
so you followed me here.

34:30.260 --> 34:31.449
Think whatever you want.

34:32.150 --> 34:34.150
If you fail to bring Bai Shuo back this time,

34:34.150 --> 34:35.570
Grand Master won't let you off.

34:35.719 --> 34:37.719
I'll do the dirty work you can't bring yourself to do.

34:37.739 --> 34:38.300
You should thank…

34:38.330 --> 34:39.730
Mind your own business.

34:39.750 --> 34:40.659
I have my own way.

34:41.900 --> 34:42.980
What way?

34:43.360 --> 34:46.199
Talking with her about old times in Ning'an City?

34:46.219 --> 34:48.380
Reminiscing about the late city governor?

34:48.409 --> 34:49.900
Don't you dare disrespect Uncle Bai!

34:52.710 --> 34:53.880
Chong Zhao,

34:54.280 --> 34:56.389
you're now part of Cold Spring Palace.

34:57.010 --> 35:00.140
The blood on your hands will never wash clean.

35:00.430 --> 35:01.730
To Bai Shuo,

35:01.750 --> 35:03.840
you're as good as someone who killed her father.

35:04.200 --> 35:05.320
Do you think

35:05.340 --> 35:08.050
she'll still care about the fragile bond you once had?

35:14.980 --> 35:17.080
Our target this time is Bai Shuo.

35:17.460 --> 35:19.600
In the Fox Clan, you must act secretly.

35:19.770 --> 35:21.480
If Chang Mei and the others find out,

35:21.500 --> 35:22.940
we'll only find ourselves in trouble.

35:23.210 --> 35:24.050
One more thing.

35:24.630 --> 35:26.130
Don't say I didn't warn you.

35:26.150 --> 35:27.460
In Jingyou Mountain,

35:27.490 --> 35:30.030
a confrontation between you and Bai Shuo is inevitable.

35:30.130 --> 35:32.730
If you're still clinging to those old feelings,

35:32.750 --> 35:34.150
your only fate

35:34.180 --> 35:35.840
will be death.

35:42.590 --> 35:44.590
Stay, not stay.

35:45.050 --> 35:47.040
Stay, not stay.

35:49.860 --> 35:50.970
Bai Shuo.

35:53.400 --> 35:54.730
We should set off.

35:57.500 --> 35:58.460
You know what?

35:58.490 --> 36:00.700
The food here is actually pretty good.

36:01.240 --> 36:01.800
Give it a try.

36:04.640 --> 36:05.680
Try some.

36:05.710 --> 36:06.480
We'll leave after you eat.

36:11.320 --> 36:12.150
I have to say,

36:12.190 --> 36:13.840
they're really tasty.

36:30.420 --> 36:31.550
Don't worry.

36:31.590 --> 36:32.400
It's just a pill

36:32.420 --> 36:34.270
that temporarily paralyzes you.

36:34.300 --> 36:35.490
It won't kill a demon.

36:37.030 --> 36:38.510
At first, I thought

36:38.550 --> 36:40.360
Fan Yue was looking for the Weak Water Stone

36:40.380 --> 36:42.460
to break his Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

36:43.710 --> 36:45.490
In the end, it's because of me.

36:46.610 --> 36:48.500
If I continue gathering Contemplations, I'll die.

36:48.680 --> 36:50.490
But if I stop gathering them, he'll die.

36:50.750 --> 36:52.100
Either way, one of us is doomed.

36:52.120 --> 36:53.370
He wants me to live,

36:54.120 --> 36:55.570
so I should let him live too.

36:57.310 --> 36:59.430
To activate the Contemplation Stone, we need to gather the Five Contemplations.

36:59.450 --> 37:00.610
If he misses this one,

37:00.640 --> 37:02.000
he might never find it again.

37:02.760 --> 37:04.140
I've come to understand

37:04.170 --> 37:05.770
Fan Yue's personality now.

37:06.330 --> 37:07.640
Most of what he says

37:07.660 --> 37:09.200
isn't truly what he feels.

37:09.430 --> 37:10.930
He cares for Tian Huo,

37:11.200 --> 37:12.800
making sure she doesn't go against her will.

37:13.140 --> 37:14.620
He also cares for you,

37:14.650 --> 37:16.590
asking the injured you to send me back.

37:16.750 --> 37:18.300
But who will care for him?

37:27.150 --> 37:28.150
That's why

37:28.730 --> 37:29.650
I can't leave.

37:30.270 --> 37:31.420
I have to protect him,

37:32.390 --> 37:34.040
just like he's protected all of us.

37:34.600 --> 37:35.510
Don't you agree?

37:39.790 --> 37:40.580
Bai Shuo.

37:41.060 --> 37:41.870
Bai Shuo!

37:43.360 --> 37:44.280
Bai Shuo!

37:59.600 --> 38:00.520
Chong Zhao?

38:20.720 --> 38:21.550
Do I look good?

38:23.280 --> 38:24.080
Wu,

38:24.240 --> 38:25.960
I'll definitely marry you in the future.

38:26.110 --> 38:27.110
And I'll give you

38:27.110 --> 38:29.150
the grandest wedding the Fox Clan has ever seen.

38:29.680 --> 38:30.720
Nonsense.

38:30.820 --> 38:32.890
My sister would never let me marry you.

38:33.440 --> 38:34.400
Really?

38:35.040 --> 38:35.960
Yes.

38:35.990 --> 38:37.110
But I don't care.

38:37.270 --> 38:38.270
I'm going to marry you no matter what.

38:49.800 --> 38:50.840
Wait a little longer.

38:51.780 --> 38:52.970
After tomorrow,

38:53.770 --> 38:54.860
I'll come to be with you.

38:55.640 --> 38:56.430
Auntie!

38:58.290 --> 38:59.000
Auntie!

38:59.030 --> 39:00.630
Tian Huo finally agreed to marry me!

39:00.650 --> 39:02.380
I'm going to marry her!

39:04.190 --> 39:05.320
I've thought about this seriously.

39:05.340 --> 39:07.450
Huo has a hard time believing in love

39:07.480 --> 39:08.890
because of her parents.

39:08.910 --> 39:10.580
I must seize this chance

39:10.610 --> 39:11.860
and let her feel my sincerity.

39:12.520 --> 39:14.170
Auntie, you've always spoiled me.

39:14.190 --> 39:15.550
You have to help me

39:15.580 --> 39:18.330
throw her the grandest wedding the Fox Clan has ever seen.

39:18.540 --> 39:19.190
And then,

39:19.210 --> 39:21.430
I'll swear in front of everyone in the clan

39:21.500 --> 39:23.220
that I'll love her for the rest of my life!

39:23.670 --> 39:24.730
You brat.

39:25.230 --> 39:27.080
Throwing a wedding like that isn't so easy.

39:27.200 --> 39:28.950
It'd take at least a month or so.

39:31.280 --> 39:32.320
How about this?

39:32.670 --> 39:33.720
Tomorrow, you'll attend the ceremony

39:33.760 --> 39:35.080
to inherit the position of chief first,

39:35.100 --> 39:35.580
and then...

39:35.610 --> 39:37.400
Why am I still inheriting your position?

39:37.420 --> 39:38.900
I'm getting married.

39:38.930 --> 39:40.290
In the future, I'll travel across

39:40.310 --> 39:41.580
the Eastern Continent with Huo.

39:41.610 --> 39:42.900
Didn't we agree that

39:42.920 --> 39:44.360
as long as Huo agreed to marry me,

39:44.390 --> 39:45.390
I'd be free?

39:52.100 --> 39:53.860
I remember it being somewhere around here.

39:54.080 --> 39:56.110
The traces in the forest are completely gone now.

39:56.260 --> 39:58.430
The Fox Clan must have deliberately covered them up.

39:58.950 --> 39:59.880
Let's split up and search.

39:59.900 --> 40:01.490
Find that tree as quickly as possible.

40:01.790 --> 40:03.000
We can't delay this further.

40:09.700 --> 40:11.680
You escaped from Cold Spring Palace?

40:11.780 --> 40:12.730
Since you're fine,

40:12.840 --> 40:14.510
why didn't you go back to Ning'an City to find me?

40:16.110 --> 40:17.470
Have you forgotten what happened

40:18.080 --> 40:18.970
in the Outlanders' City?

40:22.860 --> 40:23.920
Between Fan Yue

40:24.190 --> 40:25.160
and Chong Zhao,

40:25.670 --> 40:26.720
pick one.

40:27.030 --> 40:28.610
Whoever you choose,

40:28.630 --> 40:29.940
I can let him go.

40:30.230 --> 40:31.110
Fan Yue!

40:31.840 --> 40:32.760
I choose Fan Yue.

40:34.580 --> 40:39.030
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

40:35.400 --> 40:36.800
Back then, I chose him

40:37.360 --> 40:38.320
because he had the best chance…

40:38.320 --> 40:39.440
It was because he was powerful

40:40.300 --> 40:41.820
and I wasn't as good as him.

40:40.970 --> 40:46.440
♫Because love is thrilling♫

40:42.670 --> 40:44.740
That's why you made that choice.

40:47.080 --> 40:50.580
♫If you tear open my heart♫

40:51.380 --> 40:53.690
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

40:54.240 --> 40:58.560
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

41:00.270 --> 41:01.300
Chong Zhao.

41:01.300 --> 41:05.030
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

41:02.500 --> 41:03.580
I'm sorry.

41:04.410 --> 41:06.140
At the time, it was a matter of expediency,

41:05.370 --> 41:07.950
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

41:06.170 --> 41:07.730
but I truly did

41:07.750 --> 41:09.320
hurt your feelings.

41:08.250 --> 41:10.260
♫I want to tear apart♫

41:09.490 --> 41:10.830
You should blame me.

41:11.040 --> 41:13.830
♫This sky for you♫

41:12.390 --> 41:14.050
It's fine if you don't want to see me again.

41:14.160 --> 41:15.560
But my concern for you is real.

41:14.620 --> 41:17.680
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

41:15.650 --> 41:16.290
I...

41:18.010 --> 41:21.450
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

41:21.680 --> 41:25.290
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

41:25.440 --> 41:28.050
♫This moment feels like forever♫

41:28.380 --> 41:31.180
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

41:31.660 --> 41:35.290
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

41:35.760 --> 41:37.490
♫Even if I'll perish♫

41:36.710 --> 41:37.710
What's wrong?

41:37.800 --> 41:40.630
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

41:39.290 --> 41:40.300
I'm fine.

41:40.860 --> 41:44.180
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

41:41.480 --> 41:43.400
I've been doing well recently.

41:44.290 --> 41:45.610
Don't worry about me.

41:44.440 --> 41:52.330
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

41:45.640 --> 41:48.140
If you say that, then you definitely haven't been doing well.

41:49.250 --> 41:50.960
You've encountered something difficult,

41:50.980 --> 41:51.780
haven't you?

41:52.180 --> 41:53.040
Also,

41:53.150 --> 41:54.820
why are you here in the Fox Clan?

41:54.840 --> 41:56.480
How did you know I was here?

42:04.290 --> 42:05.640
What are you two doing?

42:12.290 --> 42:13.170
Bai Shuo.

42:14.320 --> 42:15.920
I told you to go back, but you didn't listen.

42:16.000 --> 42:18.340
Now you're here flirting with him.

42:18.600 --> 42:19.310
Bai Shuo,

42:19.830 --> 42:21.160
you've really surprised me.

42:21.800 --> 42:22.480
I...

42:26.650 --> 42:27.840
Where Shuo wants to go

42:27.840 --> 42:28.760
and what she wants to do

42:28.790 --> 42:29.940
have nothing to do with you!

42:29.960 --> 42:30.920
I'm talking with her.

42:30.920 --> 42:32.170
Who are you to interrupt?

42:32.190 --> 42:33.670
The two of us grew up together,

42:33.700 --> 42:35.270
facing life-and-death situations side by side.

42:35.930 --> 42:37.780
Her business is naturally my business.

42:39.140 --> 42:40.360
Get over yourself.

42:40.480 --> 42:41.810
Life-and-death situations?

42:42.430 --> 42:43.320
You're nothing but a loser.

42:43.320 --> 42:45.270
You're of no use to her in life-and-death situations!

42:46.840 --> 42:47.840
You'd better go back to Lanling

42:47.840 --> 42:48.780
and train for another few hundred years.

42:48.800 --> 42:49.760
Fan Yue!

42:59.850 --> 43:02.000
Don't take his words to heart.

43:02.030 --> 43:03.350
Since we've run into each other,

43:03.370 --> 43:04.570
you should come back with me.

43:04.160 --> 43:07.190
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

43:04.710 --> 43:05.110
No!

43:05.110 --> 43:05.760
No need.

43:07.690 --> 43:10.910
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

43:09.070 --> 43:10.760
There's something I need to do.

43:11.220 --> 43:14.890
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

43:11.580 --> 43:12.490
Shuo.

43:13.070 --> 43:14.400
I'll come to find you again.

43:15.050 --> 43:17.640
♫This moment feels like forever♫

43:18.160 --> 43:21.020
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

43:21.230 --> 43:24.830
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

43:25.240 --> 43:26.910
♫Even if I'll perish♫

43:26.930 --> 43:27.820
Chong Zhao!

43:27.230 --> 43:29.900
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

43:30.130 --> 43:33.490
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

43:30.190 --> 43:31.230
What are you doing?

43:31.260 --> 43:33.090
Isn't that a question I should be asking you?

43:33.830 --> 43:41.870
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

43:34.260 --> 43:36.190
Don't you think you owe me an explanation?

43:42.440 --> 43:43.720
Life-and-death situations?

43:43.920 --> 43:44.730
You're nothing but a loser.

43:44.750 --> 43:46.150
You're of no use to her in life-and-death situations!

43:46.460 --> 43:47.550
You'd better go back to Lanling

43:47.550 --> 43:48.800
and train for another few hundred years.

43:53.760 --> 43:54.800
Poor thing.

43:55.190 --> 43:56.760
You came all the way here to find her,

43:57.330 --> 43:59.880
like a stray dog returning to its old master.

44:00.670 --> 44:01.550
But unfortunately,

44:01.550 --> 44:03.510
a dog that left its home is just a wild dog.

44:03.540 --> 44:04.870
Even if it dies by the roadside,

44:04.890 --> 44:06.210
no one will spare it a glance.

44:06.240 --> 44:08.070
It was Zhen Yu who sent me to Jingyou Mountain,

44:08.130 --> 44:08.840
not…

44:08.840 --> 44:10.400
Grand Master sent you here to capture Bai Shuo.

44:10.400 --> 44:11.400
Have you made your move?

44:12.230 --> 44:13.510
It's not the right time yet.

44:13.510 --> 44:14.960
Timing isn't something you wait for.

44:15.110 --> 44:16.910
Tonight, I'll lure Fan Yue away,

44:16.930 --> 44:18.260
and you can take the chance to capture Bai Shuo.

44:18.290 --> 44:19.080
No!

44:23.650 --> 44:25.730
Tian Huo and Cang Shan are with Fan Yue.

44:26.420 --> 44:28.460
If you go alone, it'll be too dangerous.

44:33.880 --> 44:35.100
Then what do you suggest?

44:35.790 --> 44:37.180
I noticed Fan Yue rushing back

44:37.200 --> 44:38.640
from the depths of the forest.

44:39.070 --> 44:41.000
It seems they've come to Jingyou Mountain

44:41.000 --> 44:42.230
for a specific purpose.

44:42.790 --> 44:44.540
If we can sow discord between the two sides

44:44.850 --> 44:46.290
and have Chang Mei hold off Fan Yue,

44:47.210 --> 44:48.940
not only can we bring Bai Shuo back,

44:49.190 --> 44:50.280
but we might also

44:50.620 --> 44:53.090
get rid of Fan Yue for Cold Spring Palace.

44:53.940 --> 44:55.860
Divinity, I'm so impressed.

44:55.890 --> 44:56.730
When you're ruthless,

44:56.750 --> 44:58.500
even I, a demon, feel ashamed by comparison.

45:00.170 --> 45:01.130
But tell me,

45:01.150 --> 45:02.630
is killing Fan Yue

45:02.660 --> 45:04.570
for Cold Spring Palace,

45:05.030 --> 45:07.140
or is it your personal grudge at play?
